<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1614331-not-bad-for-a-debut-novel-although-i">Not bad for a debut novel, although I don&#39;t get how Jude could have gotten a &quot;shiny silver scar down the center of his chest&quot; in the end. To my understanding, he had never been struck in the chest in any way throughout the book, not by Jessica Price, Reese, Craddock or Jude&#39;s dad possessed by Craddock. Anyone?</a>
